Detailed Description

AuthMethodDescription is contains the description of an Authentication Method found in the AuthMethods.xml file. The class is created when the file is read by AuthenticationInit.init() and stored in the servlet context.

Author:
Kenneth Sharp
Version:
3.0 (released September 15, 2005)
